  "title": "External Audit Associate/ Audit Senior",
  "description": "<p>Our esteemed client in the <strong>Auditing &amp; Taxation industry</strong> is seeking a <strong>Audit Associate/ Audit Senior </strong>to join their dynamic team:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Employment Type: </strong>Permanent</li>\n  <li><strong>Position:</strong> Audit Associate/ Audit Senior</li>\n  <li><strong>Location:</strong> Central</li>\n  <li><strong>Working Hours:</strong> Monday to Friday, office hours</li>\n  <li><strong>Salary Package:</strong> Up to $4,500 + AWS + Bonus</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Support the planning, execution, and completion of audit engagements across a variety of industries.</li>\n  <li>Perform fieldwork and substantive testing in line with professional auditing standards.</li>\n  <li>Prepare clear and accurate working papers and supporting documentation.</li>\n  <li>Assist in drafting financial statements in accordance with SFRS.</li>\n  <li>Communicate with clients to obtain information and address audit-related queries.</li>\n  <li>Contribute to special projects such as due diligence reviews and agreed-upon procedures.</li>\n  <li>Ensure assignments are delivered on time and meet internal quality requirements.</li>\n  <li>For Senior role: supervise and review work performed by junior colleagues.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>At least Degree in Accounting or an equivalent professional qualification.</li>\n  <li>Minimum 1 year of relevant audit experience.</li>\n  <li>Candidates with 2+ years of experience may be considered for the Senior role.</li>\n  <li>Proficiency in MS Office (Word &amp; Excel)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Ready to apply? Here’s how:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Click the APPLY button, or</li>\n  <li>Email your resume (in MS Word or PDF format) to <a href=\"mailto:adelin@intuitrecruitment.com\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>adelin@intuitrecruitment.com</strong>.</a> Include the job title in your email subject line for prompt processing.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em><strong>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</strong></em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>By submitting your application, you consent to the collection and use of your personal data under Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Adelin Chong | EA Personnel Reg No.: R1875641</p>\n<p>Intuit Recruitment Pte Ltd | EA License No.: 25C2793</p>",
